<h1><span class="namespace" title="namespace std">std::</span><a href="/reference/ios/ios_base/">ios_base</a>::getloc</h1>
<div class="C_prototype"><pre>locale getloc() const;</pre></div><div id="I_description">Get current locale</div>
<section id="description">
Returns the <samp><a href="/locale">locale</a></samp> object currently associated with the stream.<br>
</section>
<br>
<section id="parameters">
<h3>Parameters</h3>
none <br>
</section>
<br>
<section id="return">
<h3>Return Value</h3>
The <samp><a href="/locale">locale</a></samp> object currently associated with the stream. <br>
</section>
<br>
<section id="access">
<h3>Data races</h3>
Accesses the stream object.<br>
Concurrent access to the same stream object may cause data races.<br>
</section>
<br>
<section id="exceptions">
<h3>Exception safety</h3>
<b>Strong guarantee:</b> if an exception is thrown, there are no changes in the stream.<br>
</section>
<br>
